{"type":"message","id":"4b302a04","parentId":"cdc10bfa","timestamp":"2026-03-03T09:32:58.273Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hw6q894fauev_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"query\":\"finnhub hot trending stock market news sentiment\",\"total\":5,\"results\":[{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\",\"name\":\"Market News & Sentiment\",\"description\":\"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from global news outlets covering stocks, crypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"},\"enum\":[\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"]},{\"name\":\"tickers\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols to filter articles by (e.g., AAPL,CRYPTO:BTC).\"}},{\"name\":\"topics\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Comma-separated list of topics to filter by.\"},\"enum\":[\"blockchain\",\"earnings\",\"ipo\",\"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\"financial_markets\",\"economy_fiscal\",\"economy_monetary\",\"economy_macro\",\"energy_transportation\",\"finance\",\"life_sciences\",\"manufacturing\",\"real_estate\",\"retail_wholesale\",\"technology\"]},{\"name\":\"time_from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"}},{\"name\":\"time_to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"}},{\"name\":\"sort\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Sorting method for results.\"},\"enum\":[\"LATEST\",\"EARLIEST\",\"RELEVANCE\"]},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"function\":\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":520.43,\"success_rate\":0.987}},{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.news_sentiment.retrieve.v1.7aca3c4a\",\"name\":\"Retrieve Market News & Sentiment\",\"description\":\"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and various financial topics.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The function name.\"},\"enum\":[\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"]},{\"name\":\"tickers\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols (e.g., COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD). Filters articles that mention all listed tickers.\"}},{\"name\":\"topics\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Comma-separated list of topics. Articles must cover all listed topics.\"},\"enum\":[\"blockchain\",\"earnings\",\"ipo\",\"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\"financial_markets\",\"economy_fiscal\",\"economy_monetary\",\"economy_macro\",\"energy_transportation\",\"finance\",\"life_sciences\",\"manufacturing\",\"real_estate\",\"retail_wholesale\",\"technology\"]},{\"name\":\"time_from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"}},{\"name\":\"time_to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"}},{\"name\":\"sort\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Sorting method.\"},\"enum\":[\"LATEST\",\"EARLIEST\",\"RELEVANCE\"]},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"function\":\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":660.49,\"success_rate\":0.973}},{\"tool_id\":\"eodhd.sentiments.retrieve.v1.c2c27d35\",\"name\":\"Retrieve Sentiment Data\",\"description\":\"Get sentiment scores for one or more financial instruments (stocks, ETFs, crypto) calculated from news and social media, normalized on a scale from -1 (very negative) to 1 (very positive).\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"s\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"One or more comma-separated tickers, for example: AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"}},{\"name\":\"from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Start date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"}},{\"name\":\"to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"End date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"s\":\"AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":1278.53,\"success_rate\":0.999}},{\"tool_id\":\"eodhd.news.retrieve.v1.fe8bf94c\",\"name\":\"Retrieve Financial News\",\"description\":\"Returns the latest financial news headlines and full articles for a given ticker symbol or topic tag. Requires either a ticker (s) or a tag (t). Supports filtering by date, pagination, and JSON response format.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"s\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The ticker code to retrieve news for, for example: AAPL.US\"}},{\"name\":\"t\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The topic tag to retrieve news for, for example: technology\"}},{\"name\":\"from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Start date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"}},{\"name\":\"to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"End date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"}},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Number of results to return (default: 50, minimum: 1, maximum: 1000)\"}},{\"name\":\"offset\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Offset for pagination (default: 0)\"}},{\"name\":\"fmt\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Response format, either json or xml (default: json)\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{}},\"provider_description\":\"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":1.183,\"success_rate\":0.741}},{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0\",\"name\":\"Market News & Sentiment Trending\",\"description\":\"This API returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from a large & growing selection of premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and a wide range of topics such as fiscal policy, mergers & acquisitions, IPOs, etc.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The function of your choice. In this case, function=NEWS_SENTIMENT\"},\"enum\":[\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"]},{\"name\":\"tickers\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The stock/crypto/forex symbols of your choice. For example: tickers=IBM will filter for articles that mention the IBM ticker; tickers=COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD will filter for articles that simultaneously mention Coinbase (COIN), Bitcoin (CRYPTO:BTC), and US Dollar (FOREX:USD) in their content.\"}},{\"name\":\"topics\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The news topics of your choice. For example: topics=technology will filter for articles that write about the technology sector; topics=technology,ipo will filter for articles that simultaneously cover technology and IPO in their content. Below is the full list of supported topics: Blockchain: blockchain, Earnings: earnings, IPO: ipo, Mergers & Acquisitions: mergers_and_acquisitions, Financial Markets: financial_markets, Economy - Fiscal Policy (e.g., tax reform, government spending): economy_fiscal, Economy - Monetary Policy (e.g., interest rates, inflation): economy_monetary, Economy - Macro/Overall: economy_macro, Energy & Transportation: energy_transportation, Finance: finance, Life Sciences: life_sciences, Manufacturing: manufacturing, Real Estate & Construction: real_estate, Retail & Wholesale: retail_wholesale, Technology: technology.\"}},{\"name\":\"time_from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format. For example: time_from=20220410T0130. If time_from is specified but time_to is missing, the API will return articles published between the time_from value and the current time.\"}},{\"name\":\"time_to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"}},{\"name\":\"sort\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"By default, sort=LATEST and the API will return the latest articles first. You can also set sort=EARLIEST or sort=RELEVANCE based on your use case.\"},\"enum\":[\"LATEST\",\"EARLIEST\",\"RELEVANCE\"]},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"By default, limit=50 and the API will return up to 50 matching results. You can also set limit=1000 to output up to 1000 results.\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"function\":\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":883.34,\"success_rate\":0.946}}],\"search_id\":\"8405e1c2-0618-4e61-a919-3e4fde4fd04c\",\"elapsed_time_ms\":255.89}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1289,"aggregated":"{\"query\":\"finnhub hot trending stock market news sentiment\",\"total\":5,\"results\":[{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\",\"name\":\"Market News & Sentiment\",\"description\":\"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from global news outlets covering stocks, crypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"},\"enum\":[\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"]},{\"name\":\"tickers\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols to filter articles by (e.g., AAPL,CRYPTO:BTC).\"}},{\"name\":\"topics\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Comma-separated list of topics to filter by.\"},\"enum\":[\"blockchain\",\"earnings\",\"ipo\",\"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\"financial_markets\",\"economy_fiscal\",\"economy_monetary\",\"economy_macro\",\"energy_transportation\",\"finance\",\"life_sciences\",\"manufacturing\",\"real_estate\",\"retail_wholesale\",\"technology\"]},{\"name\":\"time_from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"}},{\"name\":\"time_to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"}},{\"name\":\"sort\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Sorting method for results.\"},\"enum\":[\"LATEST\",\"EARLIEST\",\"RELEVANCE\"]},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"function\":\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":520.43,\"success_rate\":0.987}},{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.news_sentiment.retrieve.v1.7aca3c4a\",\"name\":\"Retrieve Market News & Sentiment\",\"description\":\"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and various financial topics.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The function name.\"},\"enum\":[\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"]},{\"name\":\"tickers\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols (e.g., COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD). Filters articles that mention all listed tickers.\"}},{\"name\":\"topics\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Comma-separated list of topics. Articles must cover all listed topics.\"},\"enum\":[\"blockchain\",\"earnings\",\"ipo\",\"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\"financial_markets\",\"economy_fiscal\",\"economy_monetary\",\"economy_macro\",\"energy_transportation\",\"finance\",\"life_sciences\",\"manufacturing\",\"real_estate\",\"retail_wholesale\",\"technology\"]},{\"name\":\"time_from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"}},{\"name\":\"time_to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"}},{\"name\":\"sort\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Sorting method.\"},\"enum\":[\"LATEST\",\"EARLIEST\",\"RELEVANCE\"]},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"function\":\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":660.49,\"success_rate\":0.973}},{\"tool_id\":\"eodhd.sentiments.retrieve.v1.c2c27d35\",\"name\":\"Retrieve Sentiment Data\",\"description\":\"Get sentiment scores for one or more financial instruments (stocks, ETFs, crypto) calculated from news and social media, normalized on a scale from -1 (very negative) to 1 (very positive).\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"s\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"One or more comma-separated tickers, for example: AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"}},{\"name\":\"from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Start date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"}},{\"name\":\"to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"End date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"s\":\"AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":1278.53,\"success_rate\":0.999}},{\"tool_id\":\"eodhd.news.retrieve.v1.fe8bf94c\",\"name\":\"Retrieve Financial News\",\"description\":\"Returns the latest financial news headlines and full articles for a given ticker symbol or topic tag. Requires either a ticker (s) or a tag (t). Supports filtering by date, pagination, and JSON response format.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"s\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The ticker code to retrieve news for, for example: AAPL.US\"}},{\"name\":\"t\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The topic tag to retrieve news for, for example: technology\"}},{\"name\":\"from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Start date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"}},{\"name\":\"to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"End date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"}},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Number of results to return (default: 50, minimum: 1, maximum: 1000)\"}},{\"name\":\"offset\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Offset for pagination (default: 0)\"}},{\"name\":\"fmt\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Response format, either json or xml (default: json)\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{}},\"provider_description\":\"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":1.183,\"success_rate\":0.741}},{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0\",\"name\":\"Market News & Sentiment Trending\",\"description\":\"This API returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from a large & growing selection of premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and a wide range of topics such as fiscal policy, mergers & acquisitions, IPOs, etc.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The function of your choice. In this case, function=NEWS_SENTIMENT\"},\"enum\":[\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"]},{\"name\":\"tickers\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The stock/crypto/forex symbols of your choice. For example: tickers=IBM will filter for articles that mention the IBM ticker; tickers=COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD will filter for articles that simultaneously mention Coinbase (COIN), Bitcoin (CRYPTO:BTC), and US Dollar (FOREX:USD) in their content.\"}},{\"name\":\"topics\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The news topics of your choice. For example: topics=technology will filter for articles that write about the technology sector; topics=technology,ipo will filter for articles that simultaneously cover technology and IPO in their content. Below is the full list of supported topics: Blockchain: blockchain, Earnings: earnings, IPO: ipo, Mergers & Acquisitions: mergers_and_acquisitions, Financial Markets: financial_markets, Economy - Fiscal Policy (e.g., tax reform, government spending): economy_fiscal, Economy - Monetary Policy (e.g., interest rates, inflation): economy_monetary, Economy - Macro/Overall: economy_macro, Energy & Transportation: energy_transportation, Finance: finance, Life Sciences: life_sciences, Manufacturing: manufacturing, Real Estate & Construction: real_estate, Retail & Wholesale: retail_wholesale, Technology: technology.\"}},{\"name\":\"time_from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format. For example: time_from=20220410T0130. If time_from is specified but time_to is missing, the API will return articles published between the time_from value and the current time.\"}},{\"name\":\"time_to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"}},{\"name\":\"sort\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"By default, sort=LATEST and the API will return the latest articles first. You can also set sort=EARLIEST or sort=RELEVANCE based on your use case.\"},\"enum\":[\"LATEST\",\"EARLIEST\",\"RELEVANCE\"]},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"By default, limit=50 and the API will return up to 50 matching results. You can also set limit=1000 to output up to 1000 results.\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"function\":\"N