onnect\n            - img [ref=e87]\n            - text: Finnhub Connect\n      - list [ref=e88]:\n        - listitem [ref=e89]:\n          - link \"Register\" [ref=e90] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /register\n        - listitem [ref=e91]:\n          - link \"Login\" [ref=e92] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /login\n  - generic [ref=e95]:\n    - generic [ref=e96]:\n      - heading \"Finnhub Stock API\" [level=1] [ref=e97]\n      - paragraph [ref=e98]: Democratize Financial Data with the most powerful stock API on the market.\n      - heading \"Real-Time RESTful APIs and Websocket for Stocks, Currencies, and Crypto.\" [level=2] [ref=e99]\n      - paragraph [ref=e100]: Access real-time stock API, institutional-grade fundamental and alternative data to supercharge your investment for FREE.\n    - generic [ref=e101]:\n      - link \"API Documentation\" [ref=e102] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: /docs/api\n      - link \"Get free API key\" [ref=e103] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: /register\n  - generic [ref=e104]:\n    - heading \"You're in good company\" [level=3] [ref=e105]\n    - generic [ref=e106]:\n      - img \"Google logo\" [ref=e107]\n      - img \"Coca-cola logo\" [ref=e108]\n      - img \"APG asset management\" [ref=e109]\n      - img \"Baidu logo\" [ref=e110]\n      - img \"PSBpark logo\" [ref=e111]\n      - img \"Fed logo\" [ref=e112]\n      - img \"Chino Commercial Bank logo\" [ref=e113]\n  - generic [ref=e116]:\n    - generic [ref=e117]:\n      - heading \"Fundamental Data\" [level=2] [ref=e118]\n      - link \"Finnhub stock API - fundamental data\" [ref=e120] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: /docs/api\n        - img \"Finnhub stock API - fundamental data\" [ref=e121]\n      - generic [ref=e122]:\n        - heading \"Financial statements\" [level=3] [ref=e123]:\n          - link \"Financial statements\" [ref=e124] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/financials\n        - paragraph [ref=e125]: We provide detailed financial statements for global companies going back 30+ years.\n        - paragraph [ref=e126]: 30 years of comprehensive dividends data is also available.\n      - generic [ref=e127]:\n        - heading \"Analyst's Estimates\" [level=3] [ref=e128]:\n          - link \"Analyst's Estimates\" [ref=e129] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/company-earnings\n        - paragraph [ref=e130]: Real-time earnings notifications, historical surprises, analyst's price target and upgrade/downgrades.\n      - generic [ref=e131]:\n        - heading \"Global ETFs, Mutual Funds and Indices\" [level=3] [ref=e132]:\n          - link \"Global ETFs, Mutual Funds and Indices\" [ref=e133] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/etfs-holdings\n        - paragraph [ref=e134]: Comprehensive ETFs, Mutual funds and Indices data such as profile, holdings, historical constituents and industry exposure. Global ETFs' constituent data is available on Finnhub.\n      - generic [ref=e135]:\n        - heading \"Revenue Segments & KPIs\" [level=3] [ref=e136]:\n          - link \"Revenue Segments & KPIs\" [ref=e137] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/revenue-breakdown-kpi-api\n        - paragraph [ref=e138]: Revenue segments and KPIs for 30,000+ global companies.\n    - generic [ref=e139]:\n      - heading \"Real-time Market Data\" [level=2] [ref=e140]\n      - link \"Finnhub Stock API - real-time market data\" [ref=e142] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: /docs/api\n        - img \"Finnhub Stock API - real-time market data\" [ref=e143]\n      - generic [ref=e144]:\n        - heading \"Stock API\" [level=3] [ref=e145]:\n          - link \"Stock API\" [ref=e146] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/stock-candles\n        - paragraph [ref=e147]: 30 years of historical data for US market updated in real-time. 15-minute delayed LSE data and End-of-day tick-level data for international markets are available on Finnhub.\n      - generic [ref=e148]:\n        - heading \"US Bonds\" [level=3] [ref=e149]:\n          - link \"US Bonds\" [ref=e150] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/bond-price\n        - paragraph [ref=e151]: Access delayed FINRA Trace corporate bonds at an affordable price.\n      - generic [ref=e152]:\n        - heading \"Forex API\" [level=3] [ref=e153]:\n          - link \"Forex API\" [ref=e154] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/forex-candles\n        - paragraph [ref=e155]: Get direct connection to 10+ forex brokers.\n      - generic [ref=e156]:\n        - heading \"Crypto API\" [level=3] [ref=e157]:\n          - link \"Crypto API\" [ref=e158] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/crypto-candles\n        - paragraph [ref=e159]: Access 15+ crypto brokers with a single API.\n      - generic [ref=e160]:\n        - heading \"Technical Analysis\" [level=3] [ref=e161]:\n          - link \"Technical Analysis\" [ref=e162] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/support-resistance\n        - paragraph [ref=e163]: Precomputed technical indicators, support/resistance levels, pattern recognition and aggregate indicators' signal are supported via our API.\n    - generic [ref=e164]:\n      - heading \"Alternative Data\" [level=2] [ref=e165]\n      - link \"Finnhub Stock API - alternative data - earnings call transcripts API\" [ref=e167] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: /docs/api\n        - img \"Finnhub Stock API - alternative data - earnings call transcripts API\" [ref=e168]\n      - generic [ref=e169]:\n        - heading \"Earnings Call Transcripts & Presentations\" [level=3] [ref=e170]:\n          - link \"Earnings Call Transcripts & Presentations\" [ref=e171] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/earnings-call-transcripts-api\n        - paragraph [ref=e172]: 15+ years of earnings call transcripts with downloadable audio.\n      - generic [ref=e173]:\n        - heading \"News & Social Media Sentiment\" [level=3] [ref=e174]:\n          - link \"News & Social Media Sentiment\" [ref=e175] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/news-sentiment\n        - paragraph [ref=e176]: Real-time news, reddit, twitter sentiment to help you understand where the market is heading.\n      - generic [ref=e177]:\n        - heading \"ESG Data\" [level=3] [ref=e178]:\n          - link \"ESG Data\" [ref=e179] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/company-esg-score-api\n        - paragraph [ref=e180]: Obtain latest ESG data directly from companies' annual ESG reports.\n      - generic [ref=e181]:\n        - heading \"Congressional Trading & Senate Lobbying\" [level=3] [ref=e182]:\n          - link \"Congressional Trading & Senate Lobbying\" [ref=e183] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/congressional-trading\n        - paragraph [ref=e184]: Obtain trades by congressional members and follow lobbying efforts by companies.\n  - generic [ref=e192]:\n    - text: Deep historical data\n    - heading \"Powering the most demanding applications\" [level=3] [ref=e193]\n    - paragraph [ref=e194]: \"\\\"Financial models don’t only need vast data; they also need deep past data to test historic scenarios. Why settle with 5 years of historical data or 1 market when you can have it all?\"\n    - paragraph [ref=e195]: We provide 30+ years of financial statements, 15+ years of earnings call transcripts, 30 years of historical market data, 25+ years of analysts' estimate for 65,000 global companies and much more.\n    - generic [ref=e196]:\n      - link \"Get free API key\" [ref=e197] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: /register\n      - link \"Compare Providers\" [ref=e198] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: /finnhub-stock-api-vs-alternatives\n  - generic [ref=e200]:\n    - generic [ref=e203]:\n      - heading \"Explore our data\" [level=3] [ref=e204]\n      - paragraph [ref=e205]: Learn how our instituional-grade financial data can help power your next application and trading system.\n    - generic [ref=e206]:\n      - generic [ref=e208]:\n        - img \"Finnhub Stock API - Global fundamental data\" [ref=e210]\n        - generic [ref=e212]:\n          - text: Global Fundamental Data\n          - heading \"30+ years of historical fundamentals\" [level=3] [ref=e213]\n          - link \"See Demo\" [ref=e214] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/financials\n      - generic [ref=e216]:\n        - img \"Finnhub Stock API - historical market data API\" [ref=e218]\n        - generic [ref=e220]:\n          - text: Historical Market Data\n          - heading \"30+ years of historical data, which is perfect for charting applications.\" [level=3] [ref=e221]\n          - link \"See Demo\" [ref=e222] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/stock-candles\n      - generic [ref=e224]:\n        - img \"Finnhub Stock API - Analyst's Estimate\" [ref=e226]\n        - generic [ref=e228]:\n          - text: Analysts' Estimate\n          - heading \"15+ years of historical estimates, 5 years future estimates, EPS/Sale surprises and real-time notifications.\" [level=3] [ref=e229]\n          - link \"See Demo\" [ref=e230] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/company-eps-estimates\n      - generic [ref=e232]:\n        - img \"Finnhub Stock API - Earnings call transcripts API\" [ref=e234]\n        - generic [ref=e236]:\n          - text: Earnings Call Transcripts\n          - heading \"15+ years of earnings call transcripts with downloadable audio.\" [level=3] [ref=e237]\n          - link \"See Demo\" [ref=e238] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/earnings-call-transcripts-api\n      - generic [ref=e240]:\n        - img \"Finnhub Stock API - Global ETFs constituents\" [ref=e242]\n        - generic [ref=e244]:\n          - text: Global ETFs Constituents\n          - heading \"Comprehensive global ETFs constituents data updated daily.\" [level=3] [ref=e245]\n          - link \"See Demo\" [ref=e246] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/etfs-holdings\n      - generic [ref=e248]:\n        - img \"Finnhub Stock API - company's ownership\" [ref=e250]\n        - generic [ref=e252]:\n          - text: Company's ownership\n          - heading \"Comprehensive list of shareholders and global insider transactions.\" [level=3] [ref=e253]\n          - link \"See Demo\" [ref=e254] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /docs/api/fund-ownership\n  - generic [ref=e259]:\n    - generic [ref=e260]:\n      - heading \"Horizontal Scalability & High Availability\" [level=3] [ref=e261]\n      - paragraph [ref=e262]: “Enterprise-grade technology used to power your API.\n      - paragraph [ref=e263]: 99.99% uptime with SLA available for enterprise client. Scale automatically for complex financial analysis, scale petabyte-scale analytics on demand, and reduce costs of sourcing your own data. Built by ex-engineers of Bloomberg, Google, and Tradeweb.\n    - link \"Get Started\" [ref=e264] [cursor=pointer]:\n      - /url: /register\n  - generic [ref=e266]:\n    - heading \"About Finnhub Stock API\" [level=2] [ref=e269]\n    - generic [ref=e271]:\n      - paragraph [ref=e272]:\n        - text: With the sole mission of democratizing financial data, we are proud to offer a FREE realtime API for stocks, forex and cryptocurrency. With this API, you can access realtime market data from stock exchanges, 10 forex brokers, and 15+ crypto exchanges. We also provide institutional-grade alternative and fundamental data for global companies through our stock API. We make use of state-of-the-art machine learning algorithms to collect, clean, and standardize data across global markets. See why Finnhub is the leader in financial data APIs with\n        - link \"this stock APIs comparision\" [ref=e273] [cursor=pointer]:\n          - /url: https://medium.com/@stock-api/top-5-best-stock-api-in-2021-for-fintech-startups-and-developers-dd1420339703\n        - text: .\n      - paragraph [ref=e274]:\n        - text: To get started, check out our\n        - link \"stock API documentation\" [ref=e275] [cursor=pointer]:\n          - /url: /docs/api\n        - text: and\n        - link \"get your free API key\" [ref=e276] [cursor=pointer]:\n          - /url: /register\n        - text: .\n      - generic [ref=e277]:\n        - generic [ref=e278]:\n          - paragraph [ref=e279]:\n            - generic [ref=e280]: \n            - text: \"Pricing:\"\n            - link \"Fundamental Data\" [ref=e281] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: /pricing-fundamental-data\n          - paragraph [ref=e282]:\n            - generic [ref=e283]: \n            - text: \"Pricing:\"\n            - link \"Market Data\" [ref=e284] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: /pricing-stock-api-market-data\n          - paragraph [ref=e285]:\n            - generic [ref=e286]: \n            - text: \"Pricing:\"\n            - link \"Estimates Data\" [ref=e287] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: /pricing-stock-estimates\n          - paragraph [ref=e288]:\n            - generic [ref=e289]: \n            - text: NJ, USA\n        - generic [ref=e290]:\n          - paragraph [ref=e291]:\n            - generic [ref=e292]: \n            - text: \"Sales:\"\n            - link \"sales@finnhub.io\" [ref=e293] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: mailto:sales@finnhub.io\n          - paragraph [ref=e294]:\n            - generic [ref=e295]: \n            - text: \"Technical support:\"\n            - link \"support@finnhub.io\" [ref=e296] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: mailto:support@finnhub.io\n          - paragraph [ref=e297]:\n            - generic [ref=e298]: \n            - text: \"Billing :\"\n            - link \"billing@finnhub.io\" [ref=e299] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: mailto:billing@finnhub.io\n      - generic [ref=e301]:\n        - list:\n          - listitem [ref=e302]:\n            - link \"Finnhub Stock API Facebook\" [ref=e303] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: https://www.facebook.com/Finnhub-109587983789885\n  